title: Episode 72: An Inside Look at Inside Out
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this fun episode, Dr. Ryan Martin is joined by students Taylor Gulbrand, Roz Stoa, and Paige Richardson to discuss the film "Inside Out!" They cover their likes and dislikes of the movie, its connections to psychology, stereotypes, and the relatable aspects of the film!
